<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heilman Schildknecht zu Kleinfürstenberg, Wirt des Nürnberger Hofs in Frankfurt am Main und Bürger zu Frankfurt am Main</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Fürsprache wegen Verlängerung des Waffenstillstands zwischen Nürnberg und den Herren von Hanau über Martinstag hinaus.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_315" id="157r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_315_r2l18">Heylman Schılknecht cʒu <expan>kleinfürſtenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_315_r2l19"><expan>burger<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu frankfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_315_r2l20">Lıeber 
<del rend="strikethrough">her </del> heılman / Als Markart vvaltman vnſer diener 
<del rend="strikethrough"> von </del> vormals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_315_r2l21">mit ew geredt hat / als von <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> lengern <expan>ſtallu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wegen / . cʒwiſchen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_315_r2l24">den von Hanaw vnd vnſerr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_315_r1l1">auf ſant </ab><ab facs="#facs_315_r1l2">Merteins tag </ab><ab facs="#facs_315_r1l3">oder ſo Jr </ab><ab facs="#facs_315_r1l4">lengſt mügt </ab></add>
<add><ab facs="#facs_315_line_1576494362912_9886">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſo Jr lengſt mügt </del></ab></add> Alſo bıten vvir ew <expan>fleiſſıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_315_r2l26">ew <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache 
<add><ab facs="#facs_315_line_1576494365877_9891">ernſtlich </ab></add> <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein laſſen wöllet / vnd ewch durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_315_r2l27">darunter müet / 
<del rend="strikethrough">das </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_315_line_1576494369322_9896">das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab></add> vnd vvie es v̈mb <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache geſtalt ſeẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_315_r2l28">das lat vns bey diſem boten <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vviſſen / 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> fe </del> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vıj̃ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_315_r2l29">poſt Jacobi </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_315" id="157r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Heylman Schilknecht czu <expan>Kleinfürstenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                                <expan>burger<ex>n</ex></expan> czu Frankfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Heilman, als Markart Waltman, unser diener, vormals mit ew geredt hat
                        als von <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> lengern
                            <expan>stallu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wegen czwischen den von Hanaw und
                            unserr <add><app><note><q type="date">auf sant merteins tag</q>11.11.1411</note></app> oder so ir lengst mügt</add>, also biten
                        wir ew <expan>fleissiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir ew
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache <add>ernstlich</add>
<expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen wöllet und ewch durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> darunter müet. <add>Das
                                    <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</add> Und wie es ümb
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache gestalt sey, das lat uns bey
                        disem boten <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wissen.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vii post Jacobi.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
